WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.940
=Episode 9=

01:41.660 --> 01:42.570
Tomorrow morning,

01:42.690 --> 01:44.130
go back to Qingque Sect on your own.

01:46.570 --> 01:47.410
What about you?

01:47.820 --> 01:49.500
You already figured out
how to break this.

01:49.900 --> 01:52.410
Guangtian Sect and Lord Song
will support you.

01:52.820 --> 01:53.660
I'm guessing

01:54.130 --> 01:56.130
you've already got a plan in mind.

01:57.820 --> 01:58.930
Yeah, I have.

02:02.770 --> 02:03.610
Zhao,

02:04.020 --> 02:05.260
what do you mean?

02:05.570 --> 02:07.380
Yin Dai imprisoned Elder Kaiyang

02:08.010 --> 02:09.850
to get the Ziwei Method.

02:10.340 --> 02:11.730
When you read Yin Dai's handbook,

02:12.010 --> 02:13.540
you already saw it

02:14.570 --> 02:16.130
in its hidden layer,

02:16.410 --> 02:17.250
right?

02:18.150 --> 02:19.940
The fire's dying down.
I'll go get some more.

02:19.940 --> 02:20.780
I'll do it.

02:25.620 --> 02:29.060
(Ziwei Method)

02:33.820 --> 02:34.660
What did you see?

02:37.460 --> 02:38.500
That's why you're looking

02:38.500 --> 02:39.820
for Yin Dai's handbook, right?

02:42.380 --> 02:43.620
Back in the Library dungeon,

02:43.631 --> 02:45.660
Qian Xueshen said that the antidote
was the saliva.

02:46.100 --> 02:47.420
Saliva of the Snow-Scale Beast.

02:48.380 --> 02:49.220
Where is it?

02:49.380 --> 02:51.180
In the snow mountains
in the Freezing Area.

02:51.580 --> 02:52.420
From that moment,

02:52.620 --> 02:54.180
you already had a plan

02:54.420 --> 02:55.820
to look for the saliva.

02:55.820 --> 02:57.820
The handbook must contain records

02:58.180 --> 03:00.500
that the saliva is one of the key media

03:00.500 --> 03:01.860
for cultivating the Ziwei Method.

03:03.260 --> 03:04.540
You waited for me

03:05.060 --> 03:06.946
and chased me all the way
to the snow mountains

03:07.220 --> 03:09.420
just to use me to find the saliva.

03:12.220 --> 03:13.486
You deliberately got close to me

03:14.147 --> 03:15.560
and helped me every step of the way,

03:16.580 --> 03:18.100
all for the Ziwei Method.

03:23.580 --> 03:24.420
That's right.

03:25.100 --> 03:27.660
I went to Qingque Sect
for the Ziwei Method.

03:28.860 --> 03:30.900
But since you already suspected me,

03:31.206 --> 03:33.572
why did you still let me go
to the snow mountains with you?

03:37.420 --> 03:38.260
That's because...

03:41.300 --> 03:42.300
Because you clung to me.

03:45.380 --> 03:46.820
With your intelligence and sharpness,

03:47.020 --> 03:48.213
if you wanted to shake me off,

03:48.420 --> 03:50.100
wouldn't that have been easy?

03:50.500 --> 03:51.260
You already guessed

03:51.271 --> 03:53.493
that some of the companions
were from the demonic sect.

03:53.504 --> 03:55.264
You knew this journey was dangerous,

03:55.860 --> 03:57.580
so you wanted me to protect you

03:57.580 --> 03:58.980
and help you find the saliva asap.

03:59.660 --> 04:00.740
That way,

04:00.980 --> 04:02.060
you were using me too.

04:02.540 --> 04:04.060
There's no difference between us.

04:04.513 --> 04:06.180
You know the consequences
of Nie Hengcheng

04:06.180 --> 04:07.386
cultivating the Ziwei Method.

04:07.460 --> 04:09.110
If you'll become a second Nie Hengcheng,

04:09.110 --> 04:09.980
I might as well...

04:09.980 --> 04:10.820
What?

04:12.180 --> 04:13.060
Kill me?

04:17.060 --> 04:18.506
I might as well lock you up right now

04:18.660 --> 04:19.940
to avoid future trouble.

04:20.420 --> 04:21.260
Zhao,

04:21.860 --> 04:23.100
I will never

04:23.100 --> 04:24.380
let anyone lock me up again.

04:26.540 --> 04:28.060
Perhaps it won't be long

04:29.840 --> 04:31.540
before I put your mind at ease.

05:07.540 --> 05:08.460
Mu Qingyan?

05:13.860 --> 05:15.180
The saliva hasn't decreased.

05:15.660 --> 05:16.540
Mu Qingyan?

05:17.500 --> 05:18.460
Miss, you're awake.

05:19.140 --> 05:19.980
Come.

05:20.860 --> 05:21.980
Come eat some wonton.

05:24.020 --> 05:25.140
He knocked me out

05:25.780 --> 05:27.133
and just gave me a bowl of wonton?

05:27.220 --> 05:28.700
Uncle Cheng, where is he?

05:29.860 --> 05:30.700
The Young Master said

05:31.020 --> 05:32.540
you were exhausted from traveling

05:32.540 --> 05:33.540
and should sleep soundly

05:33.780 --> 05:35.460
before you return to Qingque Sect.

05:36.340 --> 05:37.460
He went back for revenge?

05:39.100 --> 05:39.940
The Young Master said

05:40.107 --> 05:42.096
the debts of the Mu clan
across three generations

05:42.300 --> 05:44.060
should be settled with Nie.

05:45.740 --> 05:46.740
I knew it.

05:47.060 --> 05:48.340
With his temperament,

05:48.540 --> 05:50.620
he was bound to reclaim
the Chief position.

05:54.460 --> 05:56.060
If he didn't want the saliva,

05:56.900 --> 05:58.660
why did he go
to the snow mountains with me?

05:59.220 --> 06:00.820
He even risked his life.

06:01.140 --> 06:02.140
He said

06:02.426 --> 06:03.780
he couldn't let you be alone there,

06:03.780 --> 06:05.300
without anyone to rely on.

06:05.620 --> 06:07.780
He couldn't let you
gamble your life alone.

06:08.380 --> 06:10.060
You took care of the Young Master

06:10.060 --> 06:11.860
for many days at Qingque Sect.

06:12.500 --> 06:14.682
He made the wonton before he left,

06:14.693 --> 06:16.060
served with ginseng chicken soup.

06:16.060 --> 06:17.300
Eat them while they're hot.

06:28.300 --> 06:29.300
Uncle Cheng,

06:31.420 --> 06:33.300
why is there no scallion?

06:40.860 --> 06:41.700
Thank you.

06:48.300 --> 06:50.220
You complain for three days

06:50.366 --> 06:51.913
just because a wonton has no scallions.

06:52.260 --> 06:54.860
Someone so attached to worldly pleasures

06:56.260 --> 06:58.860
could hardly last three days

06:59.460 --> 07:00.780
on this cold, silent snow peak.

07:01.133 --> 07:02.580
And you want to live here long-term?

07:05.380 --> 07:06.220
Uncle Cheng,

07:07.060 --> 07:08.020
if someone...

07:09.380 --> 07:10.660
I mean, a friend of mine.

07:11.740 --> 07:14.220
If she doesn't get wonton
with scallions,

07:14.980 --> 07:16.820
she'll be angry for days.

07:18.060 --> 07:19.940
Does that count as petty?

07:21.980 --> 07:23.420
By common sense,

07:23.860 --> 07:25.540
that would indeed be petty.

07:31.860 --> 07:32.780
The Young Master

07:33.740 --> 07:35.260
ordered me to give this token

07:35.420 --> 07:36.460
to you.

07:39.820 --> 07:41.340
(Aide)
Aide of Bliss Palace?

07:41.700 --> 07:43.060
Against the Demonic Camp,

07:43.420 --> 07:45.500
this item may be of help.

07:46.480 --> 07:47.340
Miss,

07:47.340 --> 07:48.380
be extra careful.

07:53.940 --> 07:56.340
(Aide)

07:59.460 --> 08:00.860
It's too hot!

08:01.660 --> 08:03.140
Sorry, sorry.

08:03.460 --> 08:04.620
Sorry to disturb you.

08:08.620 --> 08:11.300
(Aide)

08:11.300 --> 08:13.540
Mocking me before leaving?

08:14.140 --> 08:15.020
You're the petty one.

08:15.020 --> 08:16.340
Your whole family is petty.

08:31.820 --> 08:33.340
News from the mountain foot:

08:33.860 --> 08:36.500
Reinforcements from Xuankong Nunnery
and Peiqiong Manor

08:36.500 --> 08:37.660
were blocked halfway.

08:39.540 --> 08:41.300
The demonic sect prepared in advance.

08:41.940 --> 08:43.660
If we just wait here,

08:43.860 --> 08:45.180
that won't solve anything.

08:55.500 --> 08:56.740
It's been 15 days.

08:58.100 --> 08:59.380
I don't know

08:59.500 --> 09:00.860
how Zhao is doing now.

09:16.420 --> 09:17.260
Fengchi,

09:17.820 --> 09:19.660
you brought all the juniors here.

09:20.620 --> 09:21.620
What advice do you have?

09:22.740 --> 09:23.620
Lord Song.

09:24.220 --> 09:25.300
May I ask

09:25.900 --> 09:27.860
how much longer Guangtian Sect

09:27.860 --> 09:29.140
will be guarding Qingque Sect?

09:30.420 --> 09:31.260
Uncle,

09:31.900 --> 09:34.140
I know you want to protect us,

09:34.540 --> 09:36.020
but it's already been half a month.

09:36.460 --> 09:38.386
We're confined
to the Disciples' Dorm every day.

09:38.860 --> 09:41.380
Even my mother's guards
were ordered back when they tried

09:41.660 --> 09:43.060
to go buy necessities.

09:44.180 --> 09:45.020
Uncle,

09:45.580 --> 09:47.820
you don't even trust us?

09:47.820 --> 09:48.780
It's not that.

09:48.980 --> 09:49.820
I think

09:50.260 --> 09:52.020
they want to take over Qingque Sect.

09:52.020 --> 09:52.900
Fengchi.

09:56.060 --> 09:57.740
The Qingque Sect

09:58.940 --> 10:00.060
is not in chaos yet.

10:00.300 --> 10:01.180
If so,

10:01.700 --> 10:03.140
why are we being confined here,

10:03.380 --> 10:05.660
letting Guangtian Sect
overstep its bounds?

10:06.060 --> 10:06.900
Yuzhi,

10:07.060 --> 10:09.429
are you pretending not to know,

10:09.440 --> 10:10.620
or are you secretly pleased,

10:10.620 --> 10:11.940
hoping your father

10:11.940 --> 10:13.220
could become the Lord?

10:18.420 --> 10:19.260
Nonsense.

10:21.420 --> 10:22.260
Lord Song,

10:22.860 --> 10:24.380
why get mad when I'm telling the truth?

10:24.900 --> 10:26.740
Even if there truly were a Body Shift,

10:26.740 --> 10:28.540
interrogating everyone one by one

10:28.740 --> 10:31.100
for half a month
would reveal the traitor.

10:31.540 --> 10:32.380
But what about now?

10:33.460 --> 10:34.580
You sit still and do nothing,

10:34.860 --> 10:36.900
letting Guangtian Sect
make the decisions.

10:37.180 --> 10:38.420
What is your intention?

10:38.780 --> 10:39.820
Dai,

10:40.460 --> 10:42.540
if not for the brotherhood

10:42.780 --> 10:44.220
I shared with your late father,

10:44.820 --> 10:47.489
I'd kill you for your master

10:47.500 --> 10:48.940
just for slandering fellow disciples

10:48.950 --> 10:49.790
and spreading alarm.

10:49.790 --> 10:50.650
Father.

10:52.540 --> 10:53.380
Fengchi,

10:53.940 --> 10:55.460
my family harbors no ulterior motives.

10:55.613 --> 10:56.742
Once this matter is resolved,

10:56.753 --> 10:58.140
Guangtian Sect will withdraw.

10:58.820 --> 11:00.300
If you are still uneasy,

11:02.620 --> 11:03.780
I will also leave the sect.

11:04.140 --> 11:05.220
Yuzhi,

11:05.940 --> 11:07.500
that's not what I meant.

11:09.380 --> 11:11.060
You know Master values you,

11:11.180 --> 11:12.300
and Lingbo depends on you.

11:12.420 --> 11:14.580
Why put on such a show?

11:17.860 --> 11:18.860
Foolish.

11:20.700 --> 11:22.500
I act openly and uprightly.

11:22.940 --> 11:25.380
I won't stoop to argue
with an ignorant brat like you.

11:26.940 --> 11:27.780
Fine.

11:28.540 --> 11:29.540
Let me tell you.

11:30.006 --> 11:31.513
The reason you're not allowed to leave

11:31.700 --> 11:34.500
is that I don't want outsiders to know

11:34.700 --> 11:37.100
that your master,
the Lord of the top set,

11:38.220 --> 11:40.660
was swapped by demonic sect scum.

11:42.540 --> 11:44.140
If this leaks out,

11:44.540 --> 11:46.220
how will the Six Sects

11:46.460 --> 11:48.700
ever hold their heads up
in Jianghu again?

11:48.980 --> 11:49.820
Uncle,

11:50.660 --> 11:52.820
it's impossible to swap an elite
like my father.

11:53.860 --> 11:54.820
Lord Song

11:55.380 --> 11:56.980
is merely taking advantage of us

11:57.140 --> 11:58.900
to reap the benefits.

11:58.900 --> 11:59.740
Enough.

12:05.580 --> 12:07.060
Yuzhi is still recovering.

12:07.060 --> 12:08.300
What are you doing here?

12:08.900 --> 12:09.740
All of you, go back.

12:10.820 --> 12:11.940
Yes, Lady Yin.

12:18.820 --> 12:19.660
Shijun,

12:20.580 --> 12:22.300
the juniors were reckless.

12:22.700 --> 12:23.980
Please don't take it to heart.

12:26.380 --> 12:27.940
With troubles both within and without,

12:28.620 --> 12:30.060
we trouble you

12:30.180 --> 12:31.980
to help manage sect affairs.

12:32.460 --> 12:33.380
But may I ask

12:33.860 --> 12:35.740
what your plans are next?

12:35.740 --> 12:37.500
Zhao has gone to find the antidote.

12:37.700 --> 12:39.020
Let's wait for her return.

12:39.180 --> 12:40.020
Uncle,

12:40.300 --> 12:41.780
you trust her that much?

12:44.873 --> 12:45.940
Reinforcements are blocked.

12:46.333 --> 12:47.580
Master's identity is uncertain.

12:48.940 --> 12:50.620
Right now, we can only wait for Zhao.

12:51.300 --> 12:53.500
You really think Cai Zhao
can find the antidote?

12:54.060 --> 12:54.900
Maybe by now

12:55.020 --> 12:56.060
she's already run off

12:56.060 --> 12:57.860
with that mysterious Chang Ning.

13:01.260 --> 13:02.100
Shijun,

13:04.020 --> 13:06.940
Cai Zhao is just a junior.

13:07.220 --> 13:09.060
We can't rely solely on her.

13:09.460 --> 13:10.300
Zhao...

13:10.300 --> 13:11.740
Zhao!

13:11.900 --> 13:13.740
Zhao...

13:13.740 --> 13:14.900
Lady Yin.

13:15.140 --> 13:16.020
Speak.

13:16.020 --> 13:17.220
We received a pigeon message.

13:17.580 --> 13:18.420
Zhao has found

13:18.980 --> 13:20.180
the antidote and returned.

13:20.620 --> 13:21.940
She's arrived in Qingque Town.

13:41.700 --> 13:43.180
- Xingjia.
- Zhao.

13:43.180 --> 13:44.140
How is the situation

13:44.140 --> 13:45.100
on the mountain now?

13:46.240 --> 13:47.771
Thousandfold Cliff is currently guarded

13:47.782 --> 13:49.006
by Guangtian Sect and Uncle Li.

13:49.100 --> 13:51.140
Other than me
purchasing supplies by order,

13:51.300 --> 13:52.460
no one is allowed in or out.

13:52.940 --> 13:53.573
The demonic sect

13:53.584 --> 13:55.315
doesn't know the situation
on the mountain,

13:55.326 --> 13:56.507
so they don't dare act rashly.

13:58.620 --> 13:59.940
I secretly investigated for days.

14:00.266 --> 14:01.260
At least over 100 members

14:01.260 --> 14:03.180
of the Demonic Camp
are hiding in the town.

14:03.460 --> 14:05.620
Their leader is a mysterious,
cloaked figure.

14:05.620 --> 14:06.566
His face can't be seen.

14:06.660 --> 14:08.940
I don't know if he is their leader,
Lu Chengnan.

14:09.180 --> 14:10.740
Yuzhi feared for your safety,

14:10.740 --> 14:12.153
so he asked me to wait here for you.

14:13.900 --> 14:15.580
Dissolve this bottle of saliva in water,

14:15.580 --> 14:16.900
and it will undo the Body Shift.

14:17.300 --> 14:18.140
Is this enough?

14:18.260 --> 14:19.180
Yes.

14:19.180 --> 14:20.020
Okay, I'll head back.

14:20.180 --> 14:21.020
Wait.

14:22.500 --> 14:24.920
Once the demonic sect knows
the Body Shift has been exposed,

14:24.940 --> 14:27.260
Master will lose his value.

14:27.540 --> 14:28.380
Maybe

14:29.020 --> 14:30.820
his life will be in danger.

14:30.993 --> 14:31.940
Then what should we do?

14:32.500 --> 14:34.260
Give this saliva to Yuzhi.

14:35.180 --> 14:37.180
Expose the impostor
on the mountain first.

14:37.460 --> 14:39.060
I have my own way to find master.

14:39.940 --> 14:40.820
What way?

14:41.100 --> 14:41.940
Just trust me.

14:43.220 --> 14:44.140
Be careful.

15:33.726 --> 15:34.933
The Lord is still in seclusion.

15:35.380 --> 15:36.220
He won't see anyone.

15:52.900 --> 15:54.180
Weren't you told not to come?

15:55.420 --> 15:56.780
I am you're wife.

15:57.140 --> 15:58.100
I'm going in.

15:58.660 --> 15:59.620
Who dares stop me?

15:59.893 --> 16:01.580
Not letting you come
is for your own good.

16:01.980 --> 16:02.860
Right now,

16:02.860 --> 16:04.100
this is a time of turmoil.

16:05.220 --> 16:07.660
You should rest in Double Lotus Palace.

16:07.780 --> 16:09.260
Don't come out again.

16:09.780 --> 16:10.860
You're always like this.

16:11.260 --> 16:13.700
Whenever something happens,
you make me hide away.

16:14.460 --> 16:15.980
It makes me look utterly useless.

16:16.220 --> 16:17.260
That's not what I mean.

16:17.940 --> 16:19.500
I know you want to protect me,

16:19.820 --> 16:22.020
but I'm your wife.

16:22.500 --> 16:23.700
We share honor

16:23.900 --> 16:24.940
and disgrace alike.

16:25.660 --> 16:27.860
When trouble comes,
we should face it together.

16:28.300 --> 16:30.420
How can I always rely on you?

16:31.460 --> 16:32.620
At this critical moment,

16:32.900 --> 16:34.620
with the demonic sect
watching from outside

16:34.860 --> 16:36.500
and villains sowing suspicion within,

16:36.860 --> 16:37.940
nothing can happen to you.

16:38.780 --> 16:41.740
I heard your poison injury has relapsed.

16:42.380 --> 16:43.780
Even Xiuming's medicine

16:44.260 --> 16:45.500
has been ineffective.

16:49.060 --> 16:50.420
What's in this box

16:50.580 --> 16:52.060
was gifted by an old friend.

16:52.420 --> 16:54.820
I preserved it in cold ice for years.

16:55.500 --> 16:57.860
I didn't even take it out

16:57.860 --> 16:59.380
when Yuzhi was injured.

17:04.820 --> 17:06.540
Back then, this old friend

17:06.900 --> 17:08.700
traveled through beaches and ravines,

17:08.980 --> 17:10.660
deep into deserts and miasma forests,

17:11.220 --> 17:12.860
risking countless dangers,

17:13.540 --> 17:15.100
just to refine

17:15.860 --> 17:17.140
one Clearing Pill.

17:19.220 --> 17:20.380
It's said this medicine

17:20.780 --> 17:22.260
can warm sinews and activate meridians

17:22.380 --> 17:23.380
and enhance cultivation.

17:23.620 --> 17:24.740
It's truly rare in the world.

17:27.140 --> 17:27.980
Yunke,

17:28.860 --> 17:30.540
this medicine will surely help you

17:31.260 --> 17:32.660
recover completely.

17:33.380 --> 17:34.780
Take it now.

17:35.420 --> 17:36.260
Dear,

17:36.940 --> 17:38.140
I just took another pill.

17:38.740 --> 17:39.620
I'll take this

17:40.740 --> 17:41.580
later.

17:47.060 --> 17:47.900
Yunke.

17:48.900 --> 17:50.140
I'm willing

17:50.580 --> 17:51.780
to weather storms with you.

17:53.460 --> 17:54.740
Will you trust me?

17:58.740 --> 17:59.580
Yes.

18:00.020 --> 18:00.860
I trust you.

18:23.140 --> 18:23.980
Hurry.

18:32.580 --> 18:33.660
Zhuang.

18:33.660 --> 18:34.500
What's wrong?

18:50.180 --> 18:51.020
Dalou.

18:54.860 --> 18:55.700
Dalou.

18:57.260 --> 18:58.100
Master.

18:59.060 --> 18:59.900
Where is Master?

19:03.260 --> 19:04.100
Dalou.

19:04.380 --> 19:05.220
Dalou.

19:11.820 --> 19:13.540
Sorry, we're closed for the day.

19:13.540 --> 19:14.500
(Aide)

19:15.140 --> 19:15.980
The aide token.

19:17.500 --> 19:19.180
Greetings, Aide.

19:19.740 --> 19:21.580
News from Thousandfold Cliff
has been sealed.

19:21.780 --> 19:23.420
The Chief fears something wrong

19:23.620 --> 19:25.140
and ordered me to escort the hostages

19:25.580 --> 19:27.020
to Hanhai Mountains

19:27.780 --> 19:28.980
for disposal by Bliss Palace.

19:29.540 --> 19:30.940
But the strategist ordered

19:30.940 --> 19:32.500
that no one may approach the hostages.

19:34.900 --> 19:36.140
By the Chief's order,

19:37.820 --> 19:39.580
you dare disobey?

19:40.140 --> 19:41.300
We wouldn't dare.

19:41.900 --> 19:43.860
But we still need
to report to the strategist.

19:46.580 --> 19:48.620
You're putting the strategist
before the Chief?

19:48.980 --> 19:50.060
Are you plotting rebellion?

19:50.159 --> 19:51.466
- Of course not.
- Of course not.

19:52.420 --> 19:53.260
Lead the way at once.

19:53.380 --> 19:54.220
- Yes.
- Yes.

19:54.620 --> 19:55.460
This way, please.

20:10.900 --> 20:11.740
Which one?

20:17.020 --> 20:17.980
Leave me.

20:22.260 --> 20:23.140
Didn't you hear me?

20:23.380 --> 20:24.220
- Yes.
- Yes.

20:47.260 --> 20:48.100
Master.

20:58.860 --> 20:59.700
Master?

21:04.460 --> 21:05.300
Qinong.

21:06.580 --> 21:08.780
What are you doing here,
instead of watching

21:09.460 --> 21:10.740
Chen Shu find the saliva?

21:15.180 --> 21:17.180
I'm acting on the Chief's orders

21:18.540 --> 21:19.620
to take your life.

21:25.900 --> 21:26.740
Master.

21:44.300 --> 21:45.220
Don't pursue.

21:46.620 --> 21:47.540
Let's go back now.

22:00.620 --> 22:02.380
(Righteous Spirit)
Shijun,

22:02.580 --> 22:03.900
what do you mean by this?

22:04.780 --> 22:06.540
You're a fake lord.

22:06.540 --> 22:07.860
Who exactly are you?

22:07.980 --> 22:10.260
Hurry up and reveal your true form.

22:10.700 --> 22:12.020
We can talk things out.

22:12.940 --> 22:13.900
Shijun,

22:14.620 --> 22:15.940
what nonsense are you spouting?

22:16.700 --> 22:18.300
Don't let the demonic sect deceive you

22:18.620 --> 22:21.660
and damage the friendship
between the two sects.

22:21.860 --> 22:23.300
Then we'll strip off your fake skin.

22:30.260 --> 22:31.100
Master.

22:32.140 --> 22:34.020
The real one has returned.

22:34.020 --> 22:35.260
You counterfeit

22:35.260 --> 22:36.820
should stop resisting stubbornly.

22:40.940 --> 22:41.940
Zhao,

22:43.300 --> 22:44.980
did you take Qian Xueshen away

22:45.260 --> 22:48.780
just to fabricate a fake master?

22:50.180 --> 22:51.220
How shameless.

22:51.780 --> 22:53.260
Your talent for turning the tables

22:53.271 --> 22:54.694
is even better than a storyteller's.

22:54.780 --> 22:55.980
To tell who's the real one,

22:56.380 --> 22:57.780
you can both drink

22:58.100 --> 22:59.020
the antidote.

23:04.500 --> 23:05.860
This isn't an antidote

23:06.380 --> 23:07.500
but poison.

23:07.940 --> 23:09.020
Dodging the issue

23:09.140 --> 23:10.180
only raises more suspicion.

23:10.700 --> 23:12.100
Please, you two,

23:12.420 --> 23:13.500
drink it together.

23:14.820 --> 23:15.860
Wenxun,

23:17.260 --> 23:19.060
you don't even trust me now?

23:20.460 --> 23:21.940
Back then in the great war,

23:22.580 --> 23:23.420
who carried you

23:23.780 --> 23:25.980
out of a pile of corpses?

23:28.220 --> 23:29.380
This farce

23:29.620 --> 23:30.580
has gone on long enough.

23:30.780 --> 23:32.500
If you truly think I'm fake,

23:32.513 --> 23:33.900
invite the heads of the Six Sects

23:34.060 --> 23:35.700
and all righteous figures of Jianghu

23:35.700 --> 23:37.140
to Qingque Sect.

23:37.500 --> 23:38.420
When that time comes,

23:38.780 --> 23:39.940
right and wrong

23:40.140 --> 23:41.420
will judge themselves.

23:41.660 --> 23:42.820
Qiu,

24:02.140 --> 24:03.060
this Clearing Pill

24:03.780 --> 24:05.700
will surely help you recover.

24:05.820 --> 24:07.220
Hurry and take it.

24:23.700 --> 24:24.900
Long time no see.

24:25.300 --> 24:26.300
I hope you've been well.

24:40.620 --> 24:43.580
(Qiu Renjie, Qingque Sect)

24:44.060 --> 24:44.980
Qiu?

24:47.980 --> 24:49.220
Qiu Renjie?

24:51.140 --> 24:53.380
You guessed it was me.

24:53.660 --> 24:56.020
Thank you for gifting me
the Clearing Pill.

25:01.820 --> 25:07.620
(Young Yin Sulian, Qingque Sect)

25:07.700 --> 25:11.460
(Young Qiu Renjie, Qingque Sect)

25:19.133 --> 25:20.180
This is the Clearing Pill.

25:20.500 --> 25:22.339
It replenishes marrow
and boosts cultivation.

25:22.460 --> 25:23.580
When you practice,

25:24.020 --> 25:25.473
you'll make advancements more easily.

25:26.620 --> 25:27.460
Qiu,

25:27.580 --> 25:28.420
you're so kind.

25:32.060 --> 25:33.300
You neither ate nor drank.

25:33.700 --> 25:35.260
If I didn't resort to this method,

25:35.620 --> 25:37.460
how could I expose your true face?

25:44.060 --> 25:46.020
You still chose him.

25:51.420 --> 25:52.260
Qiu,

25:52.740 --> 25:54.260
you disappeared for many years.

25:54.860 --> 25:56.660
We all thought you were dead.

25:56.900 --> 25:58.020
Since you're alive,

25:58.020 --> 25:59.420
why didn't you return?

25:59.580 --> 26:01.900
Why collude with the demonic sect

26:02.260 --> 26:04.300
and commit such fratricidal acts?

26:04.940 --> 26:06.220
Fratricidal?

26:09.940 --> 26:10.860
Qi Yunke,

26:11.580 --> 26:14.420
you stole my position
and took my fiancée.

26:14.900 --> 26:17.380
Whose brother would be like that?

26:18.740 --> 26:19.580
Qiu,

26:20.380 --> 26:23.620
if you're resentful about losing to me,

26:23.620 --> 26:26.020
I'm willing to compete with you again.

26:28.420 --> 26:32.060
You really are the one
that Yin Dai favored.

26:32.220 --> 26:34.820
What a hypocrite.

26:35.460 --> 26:36.300
Qiu,

26:37.140 --> 26:38.660
that's water under the bridge.

26:39.020 --> 26:40.420
Why cling to the past

26:40.820 --> 26:42.060
and slander Lord Yin Dai?

26:42.060 --> 26:43.500
Slander him?

26:44.500 --> 26:45.700
Everything I am today

26:46.940 --> 26:49.500
is entirely thanks to him.

26:51.220 --> 26:52.900
I lost back then; so be it.

26:53.460 --> 26:54.820
I could have left.

26:55.580 --> 26:58.300
But Yin deliberately sent me

26:58.300 --> 27:00.900
to Youming Path to gather intel.

27:01.580 --> 27:04.700
I was ambushed by the demonic sect
and almost died.

27:05.780 --> 27:08.460
The fellow disciples
who promised to meet me

27:08.700 --> 27:10.740
never showed up.

27:11.940 --> 27:14.180
Yin feared I wouldn't submit

27:15.500 --> 27:18.580
and wanted to use the demonic sect
to get rid of me

27:18.860 --> 27:20.540
to clear the way

27:20.540 --> 27:22.980
for his son-in-law and for himself.

27:23.260 --> 27:25.300
You're just smearing my grandfather.

27:25.300 --> 27:26.220
Do you have any proof?

27:26.460 --> 27:27.380
Proof?

27:27.700 --> 27:30.260
If your grandfather
were truly upright and selfless,

27:30.260 --> 27:32.940
why did he steal Cai Pingshu's credit?

27:35.100 --> 27:35.980
What do you mean?

27:37.220 --> 27:38.300
What credit did he steal?

27:39.213 --> 27:40.220
In the Battle of Mount Tu,

27:40.220 --> 27:42.700
Cai Pingshu killed Nie Hengcheng.

27:42.860 --> 27:45.900
Yet Yin Dai held a victory banquet

27:45.900 --> 27:48.740
and claimed the merit for himself.

27:48.740 --> 27:50.540
It was my aunt who killed Nie Hengcheng.

27:51.020 --> 27:52.100
How did it become his doing?

27:53.260 --> 27:54.100
That's right.

27:54.860 --> 27:57.420
Everyone knew about the battle

27:57.420 --> 27:58.820
between them.

28:01.180 --> 28:02.420
That was later talk.

28:03.260 --> 28:04.700
At the banquet back then,

28:05.060 --> 28:06.780
it was Yang Yi, the Lord of Siqi Sect,

28:06.780 --> 28:07.740
your grandfather,

28:07.740 --> 28:09.420
who said it was Lord Yin Dai's merit.

28:09.580 --> 28:11.780
Lord Yin Dai casually accepted it.

28:12.220 --> 28:13.980
After that, everyone said

28:14.380 --> 28:17.100
that Lord Yin Dai killed Nie Hengcheng.

28:20.380 --> 28:22.140
But he didn't benefit for long.

28:22.420 --> 28:23.740
Just a few months later,

28:23.860 --> 28:24.980
Lord Yin Dai

28:24.980 --> 28:27.220
was ambushed by Zhao Tianba,

28:27.220 --> 28:28.580
Nie Hengcheng's first disciple,

28:28.700 --> 28:30.220
and hacked to death.

28:30.220 --> 28:31.220
And then?

28:31.380 --> 28:34.380
Yin Qinglian feared being implicated.

28:34.660 --> 28:36.100
To protect Yin Dai's grandchild,

28:36.100 --> 28:37.220
her own son,

28:37.500 --> 28:39.020
she diverted the calamity elsewhere

28:39.380 --> 28:41.980
and leaked the news
that Cai Pingshu killed Nie Hengcheng

28:42.540 --> 28:43.940
to the demonic sect.

28:44.300 --> 28:46.180
No wonder they attacked Luoying Valley.

28:46.660 --> 28:48.500
If not for Uncle Chang and Master

28:48.500 --> 28:49.700
eliminating Zhao Tianba...

28:49.820 --> 28:52.260
Luoying Valley would've been wiped out.

28:53.020 --> 28:53.980
Afterward,

28:54.380 --> 28:56.380
Yin Qinglian shamelessly claimed

28:56.620 --> 28:59.820
that Lord Yin Dai
only reluctantly accepted

28:59.820 --> 29:02.380
to protect Luoying Valley.

29:02.780 --> 29:04.580
That even earned Yin

29:04.940 --> 29:07.940
the title of the Pillar
of Righteousness.

29:08.580 --> 29:09.860
Lady Qinglian

29:10.580 --> 29:11.700
really had a sharp mind.

29:13.260 --> 29:14.100
Today,

29:14.300 --> 29:16.140
I will let these juniors

29:16.380 --> 29:18.300
and the entire world know

29:18.300 --> 29:20.020
the true face of Yin

29:20.020 --> 29:20.980
and see

29:20.980 --> 29:23.180
these hypocrites and frauds.

29:23.180 --> 29:24.020
Qiu.

29:28.420 --> 29:30.140
Please stop talking.

29:35.580 --> 29:37.820
Even if Lord Yin Dai wronged you,

29:38.286 --> 29:39.620
you colluded with the demonic sect

29:39.631 --> 29:41.089
and harmed your fellow sect members.

29:41.100 --> 29:42.700
Is that really not wrong?

29:47.860 --> 29:49.860
I know my sins are grave.

29:51.540 --> 29:54.100
When I was on the brink of death,

29:55.620 --> 29:57.500
it was Nie Zhe who saved me.

29:59.460 --> 30:02.500
A man lives for those who know him.

30:06.660 --> 30:09.100
Even if I submit to the demonic sect,

30:10.700 --> 30:12.140
so what?

30:12.140 --> 30:14.340
(Righteous Spirit)

30:19.860 --> 30:21.140
That's still better

30:23.540 --> 30:26.540
than being deceived

30:28.860 --> 30:30.780
and used.

30:34.700 --> 30:35.620
Qiu,

30:36.300 --> 30:37.940
I know you were misled by villains

30:37.940 --> 30:39.100
and have your hardships.

30:39.700 --> 30:42.180
Confess the demonic sect's later schemes

30:42.180 --> 30:43.180
and make amends.

30:43.740 --> 30:45.180
I can let bygones be bygones.

30:52.980 --> 30:55.260
I can afford

30:57.060 --> 30:59.260
to lose.

31:02.460 --> 31:03.500
He'll kill himself!

31:12.220 --> 31:15.420
(Righteous Spirit)

31:24.860 --> 31:25.700
Mother!

31:25.900 --> 31:26.740
Mother.

31:26.980 --> 31:27.820
Mother!

31:28.220 --> 31:29.060
Mother.

31:34.540 --> 31:41.460
(Pillar of Righteousness)

31:52.260 --> 31:56.620
(Pillar of Righteousness)

32:01.180 --> 32:03.580
(Pillar of Righteousness)

32:05.500 --> 32:06.620
I noticed long ago.

32:07.180 --> 32:09.020
Gilded gold is the weakest.

32:15.140 --> 32:16.060
Zhao,

32:17.940 --> 32:19.060
the Yins

32:20.180 --> 32:21.540
owe Luoying Valley an apology.

32:22.900 --> 32:23.900
You're different

32:24.940 --> 32:25.780
from them.

32:46.500 --> 32:48.180
When I was young, my aptitude was poor.

32:48.580 --> 32:49.860
I could never break through.

32:50.980 --> 32:53.900
Back then, this old friend
traveled through beaches and ravines,

32:54.100 --> 32:55.980
deep into deserts and miasma forests,

32:56.540 --> 32:58.020
risking countless dangers,

32:58.500 --> 33:01.820
just to refine one Clearing Pill.

33:02.260 --> 33:03.620
Your old friend

33:04.060 --> 33:05.500
was truly thoughtful.

33:06.720 --> 33:11.910
♪If we never met♪

33:13.190 --> 33:18.760
♪Would there be no longing♪

33:19.760 --> 33:22.000
♪In that fleeting moment♪

33:22.630 --> 33:25.630
♪Within this lifetime♪

33:26.290 --> 33:28.540
♪We already brushed past♪

33:29.700 --> 33:30.660
I pray

33:31.620 --> 33:32.780
to stay together forever

33:33.220 --> 33:34.380
with Qiu.

33:39.360 --> 33:41.730
♪Love and hate, scattered in threads♪

33:41.730 --> 33:46.050
♪Intertwined and tangled into lines♪

33:47.060 --> 33:48.580
I pray to spend every day and night

33:49.380 --> 33:50.540
with Sulian.

33:52.980 --> 33:55.590
♪After parting♪

33:56.220 --> 33:58.540
♪Before death♪

33:59.660 --> 34:04.530
♪We meet no more♪

34:08.660 --> 34:10.700
(Righteous Spirit)

34:14.500 --> 34:15.420
Yunke.

34:31.240 --> 34:33.700
♪Love and hate, scattered in threads♪

34:33.700 --> 34:37.890
♪Intertwined and tangled into lines♪

34:38.500 --> 34:40.190
♪With sandstorms filling the sky♪

34:40.190 --> 34:44.470
♪I can still recognize your face♪

34:44.990 --> 34:47.750
♪After this life♪

34:48.310 --> 34:50.640
♪Before the next rebirth♪

34:51.630 --> 34:56.490
♪We meet no more♪

34:57.060 --> 35:04.060
♪I only wish to remember your face♪

35:06.460 --> 35:09.620
(The turmoil within Qingque
has been settled.)

35:09.620 --> 35:13.300
(Miss Cai is unharmed.)

35:19.980 --> 35:20.820
Young Master,

35:20.980 --> 35:21.980
they're here.

35:37.500 --> 35:39.780
(Carefree)
Welcome back, Young Master.

35:40.980 --> 35:42.940
I've waited anxiously for over a year;

35:42.940 --> 35:44.020
at last, today has come.

35:44.620 --> 35:45.673
(Carefree)
Over a year ago,

35:46.300 --> 35:49.420
Elder Tianquan Qiu Baigang
aided my uprising, which failed.

35:50.500 --> 35:52.700
Almost no one
from Elder Qiu's line survived.

35:53.420 --> 35:54.820
I did not summon you before

35:55.180 --> 35:56.780
because I could barely protect myself

35:57.060 --> 35:59.140
and didn't want you to die with me.

36:00.140 --> 36:01.820
Now that you've answered the call,

36:03.220 --> 36:04.500
you surely know

36:05.020 --> 36:06.220
what I intend to do.

36:06.679 --> 36:09.420
Nie Hengcheng and his followers
usurped power for three generations.

36:09.660 --> 36:11.220
Their influence runs deep and tangled.

36:11.740 --> 36:14.020
Killing one or two
would never turn the tide.

36:14.540 --> 36:15.380
So,

36:16.140 --> 36:18.660
this journey will surely be full

36:19.180 --> 36:20.700
of blood and corpses.

36:22.900 --> 36:24.260
Rest assured.

36:25.300 --> 36:28.060
Though the poison
of the Sevens Pill is fierce,

36:28.220 --> 36:29.420
as long as you

36:29.740 --> 36:31.300
are loyal to the Young Master,

36:31.540 --> 36:34.380
the antidote will be delivered on time.

37:08.620 --> 37:10.580
(Carefree)

37:11.020 --> 37:12.820
We swear to follow the Young Master.

37:13.780 --> 37:15.660
We swear to follow the Young Master.

37:16.460 --> 37:18.460
We swear to follow the Young Master.

37:18.860 --> 37:20.180
Pledge loyalty to the Mu clan.

37:20.300 --> 37:21.740
Unify Jianghu.

37:21.860 --> 37:23.260
Pledge loyalty to the Mu clan.

37:23.260 --> 37:24.660
Unify Jianghu.

37:24.860 --> 37:26.020
Pledge loyalty to the Mu clan.

37:26.300 --> 37:27.660
Unify Jianghu.

37:27.980 --> 37:29.220
Pledge loyalty to the Mu clan.

37:29.460 --> 37:30.940
Unify Jianghu.

37:32.640 --> 37:43.300
=Generation to Generation=

38:02.060 --> 38:06.470
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

38:07.035 --> 38:11.650
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

38:11.990 --> 38:16.555
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

38:17.080 --> 38:21.380
♪Free to wander in the world♪

38:24.325 --> 38:29.025
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

38:29.550 --> 38:33.840
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

38:34.500 --> 38:38.530
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

38:38.845 --> 38:43.970
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

38:44.545 --> 38:49.355
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

38:49.570 --> 38:53.740
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

38:54.465 --> 38:58.400
♪I freely roam in the world♪

38:58.900 --> 39:04.175
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

39:26.905 --> 39:32.035
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

39:32.400 --> 39:36.770
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

39:37.035 --> 39:41.165
♪I freely roam in the world♪

39:41.350 --> 39:46.925
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
